(The trust bootstrap for a newly arriving agent is intentionally simple: the message is) Tj
1 0 0 1 72 690 Tm
(validated using the secret transported with the agent. This is enough for a first) Tj
1 0 0 1 72 676 Tm
(demonstrator but not enough for hostile networks. A production system should move toward) Tj
1 0 0 1 72 662 Tm
