1 0 0 1 72 592 Tm
(documents. A travelling scout agent is deployed on the root node with the query "scacchi".) Tj
1 0 0 1 72 578 Tm
(It searches locally, inspects the federation tree, clones itself into each child, and) Tj
1 0 0 1 72 564 Tm
(collects distributed findings close to where the documents live. The same pattern can be) Tj
1 0 0 1 72 550 Tm
(generalized to indexing, compliance inspection, software inventory, or environment) Tj
1 0 0 1 72 536 Tm
(diagnostics.) Tj
